[Changes for 0.03 - 2007-09-04]

* Minor tidying up for Perl 5.9 compatibility.

[Changes for 0.03 - 2004-10-07]

* Declare ourselves as unsuited for PerlIO::encoding use.

[Changes for 0.02 - 2004-10-07]

* Added I/O-specific encodings like "LF-Native", which means decoding to LF
  and encoding to Native; this what "svn:eol-style = native" means.

[Changes for 0.01 - 2004-10-06]

* Initial release to CPAN.
